python manage.py startapp (app_name)








#what is http protocol:
#where are requesting something and getting something is called http protocol.

it has may request methods like:

get,post,put,delete,head,connect,option,trace,patch

GET:

where ever you want fetch from the server.

post:

is to add the data to the server.

put:

is to update the data in the server.





